<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bake Abroad | Sign Up</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/custom.css">
</head>
<body class="sign-up">
    <header class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <h2 class="fs-1 fw-bold" ><%=title%></h2>
            </a>
            <button
            class="navbar-toggler"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
            aria-controls="navbarNav"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link fs-4" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link fs-4 " href="/recipes"> Recipes </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link fs-4 active" aria-current="page" href="/signUp">Sign Up</a>
                  </li>
            </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="container-fluid pt-4 mt-4">
            <h2>Disclaimer:</h2>
            <div class="intro-text pt-4 mt-4">
                <p class="fs-5">Bake Abroad operates solely as a demonstration platform and does not engage in the provision of actual products or services. All materials and content showcased on this platform are intended strictly for educational and illustrative purposes.</p>
                <!-- <p class="fs-5">The content displayed on Bake Abroad, including but not limited to recipes and information, is sourced for educational demonstration and illustration purposes only. We do not offer any real products or services for sale or distribution.</p> -->
                <p class="fs-5">Please note that all content on this website has been sourced from
                    <a class="link" href="https://amopaocaseiro.com.br/receitas/" target="_blank">Amo Pao Caseiro Recipes</a>
                    and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@amopaocaseiro" class="link" target="_blank">Amo Pao Caseiro YouTube channel</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>        
    <div class="container pt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
                <h2 class="text-center">Sign Up</h2>
                <form name="signUp" action="/auth/signUp" method="POST" class="mt-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="username" class="form-label">Username</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="username" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <button type="submit" value="jane" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="container-fluid p-5 text-center">
        <p>
          &copy; This site is created for demonstrative purposes only and does
          not offer any real products or services.
        </p>
        The entirety of the content presented within this project has been sourced from:
        <a class="link" href="https://amopaocaseiro.com.br/receitas/">Amo Pao Caseiro Recipes</a> 
                and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@amopaocaseiro" class="link">Amo Pao Caseiro YouTube channel</a>
        </p>
      </footer>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</main>
</body>
</html>
